java.util.jar
类 JarFile

java.lang.Object
  java.util.zip.ZipFile
      java.util.jar.JarFile

public class JarFile
extends ZipFile

JarFile is used to read jar entries and their associated data from jar files.

从以下版本开始：
Android 1.0
另请参见：
JarInputStream, JarEntry

getManifest

                     throws IOException
